title: Florida friendlier than Hawaii? You are kidding, right?
text:
Florida friendlier than Hawaii? You are kidding, right? Adv: 
Jul 24, 2015 Adv: 
NEW YORK, NY - Traveling to a new city can be exhilarating and intimidating at the same time but a warm greeting and friendly smile can put all fears aside when visiting to a new destination. A new poll released by Travelzoo reveals which destinations greet travelers with open arms. 
Friendliest U.S. States 
When it comes to the East Coast/ West Coast rivalry, the East is the coast with the friendliest states. 
1. Florida
